sonusAccountingServicesMIB.description: The MIB Module for Accounting Services Management.

sonusAcctGenerationMode.name: sonusAcctGenerationMode
sonusAcctGenerationMode.description: This configures the accounting generation mode for the node

sonusAcctLogDestination.name: sonusAcctLogDestination
sonusAcctLogDestination.description: This configures the destination of the accounting files for the node

sonusAcctIntAcctState.name: sonusAcctIntAcctState
sonusAcctIntAcctState.description: This configures whether Intermediate Accounting is Enabled or Disabled for the Node

sonusAcctIntAcctInterval.name: sonusAcctIntAcctInterval
sonusAcctIntAcctInterval.description: This configures the Intermediate Accounting Interval in seconds

sonusAcctNumCallAttempts.name: sonusAcctNumCallAttempts
sonusAcctNumCallAttempts.description: The total Number of Call Attempts since last reboot

sonusAcctNumCallCompletions.name: sonusAcctNumCallCompletions
sonusAcctNumCallCompletions.description: The total Number of Succesful Call Completions since last reboot

sonusAcctNumCallAttemptFailures.name: sonusAcctNumCallAttemptFailures
sonusAcctNumCallAttemptFailures.description: The total Number of Unsuccesful Call Attempts since last reboot

sonusAcctBusyHourAttempts.name: sonusAcctBusyHourAttempts
sonusAcctBusyHourAttempts.description: The Average BHCA rate in the last one hour

sonusAcctCallAttemptRate.name: sonusAcctCallAttemptRate
sonusAcctCallAttemptRate.description: The Call arrival rate in calls/sec in the last one minute

sonusAcctAvgCallDuration.name: sonusAcctAvgCallDuration
sonusAcctAvgCallDuration.description: The Average Call Duration in seconds

sonusAcctNumCallAttemptBlocked.name: sonusAcctNumCallAttemptBlocked
sonusAcctNumCallAttemptBlocked.description: The total Number of Calls which were blocked/screened since last reboot

sonusAcctOutOfServiceReason.name: sonusAcctOutOfServiceReason
sonusAcctOutOfServiceReason.description: The Reason for Call Accounting for the Node being Out-of-Service.

sonusCallAccountingInServiceNotification.name: sonusCallAccountingInServiceNotification
sonusCallAccountingInServiceNotification.description: This Trap is Generated when a change is made to the Accounting Configuration for the Node, and the resultant configuration state of accounting for the node is that it is enabled/in-service

sonusCallAccountingOutOfServiceNotificat.name: sonusCallAccountingOutOfServiceNotification
sonusCallAccountingOutOfServiceNotificat.description: This Trap is Generated when Accounting Records are no longer being generated on the Node. It could be either because of a change to the Accounting Configuration or because of errors in the logging mechanism such as file logging errors. When the reason specified for accounting outofservice is event logging error, then the SYS event logs on the Node should be examined to obtain further information about the event logging failure
